OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Flight and patchy rain possible during
OL,7,Fthe evening, but this easing overnight
OL,8,Fwith clear spells developing. Clouding
OL,9,Fover again towards dawn with rain
OL,10,Farriving in the west. Becoming breezy,
OL,11,Fespecially on the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FCloudy this morning with
OL,14,Frain spreading eastwards, perhaps with
OL,15,Fthe odd heavier burst. Rain clearing
OL,16,Feast by early afternoon, leaving sunny
OL,17,Fspells with isolated showers
OL,18,Fdeveloping later, these occasionally
OL,19,Fheavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
